data.description:
Investor Special: Welcome to your dream horse property! This exceptional home anchored within a serene and picturesque countryside, is ready for the next owners to make their dreams come true. Offering tranquility and seclusion, don't miss your opportunity to experience nature and life's simple pleasures from the leisure of your own front door. 

Step inside to discover cozy, yet spacious family living, with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an additional bonus bedroom nook that offers versatility as a nursery, kids room, office or exercise space. The vaulted beam ceiling and fireplace in this 2-story home add even more charm and potential to its list of ingredients for an exceptional abode or getaway, all while still not far from amenities, the Sequoia National Park and still within the city of Visalia, CA.

Additionally, this property is sure to satisfy all of your equine needs, as it is fully equipped with corrals, pasture and space to easily accommodate and care for your beloved animal companions. Your horses will enjoy the wide-open space to roam and graze, ensuring their health and happiness. Additionally, there is an RV hook-up area nestled in lush oak and shaded mature trees, providing a convenient space for visiting guests or your own recreational vehicle. Do not sleep on this one, be sure to have a look for yourself.
